sub_title: MSc Student Clinical Research | Student Researcher at Dept. of Interventional Cardiology | Erasmus MC & NIHES
summary: I am an ambitious fourth year medical student and clinical research student at the Erasmus University Medical Center, Rotterdam. Because of my strong interest in the fields of clinical medicine and (bio)medical research, I have chosen to develop myself in these areas. I do this by being involved in a variety of projects. At the moment my main position is as a student researcher at the department of interventional cardiology.
